<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 01:08:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>用月球泥土 3D 打印月球栖息地</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/3d-printing-with-moon-dirt-for-lunar-habitats</link><description>“通过在打印过程中结合金属和陶瓷等不同原料，我们发现最终材料对环境非常敏感，”徐思哲说。 [&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/3d-printing-with-moon-dirt-for-lunar-habitats.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 01:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/3d-printing-with-moon-dirt-for-lunar-habitats</guid></item><item><title>通过共享数据和生物样本加强临床癌症研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/enhancing-clinical-cancer-research-through-sharing-of-data-and-biospecimens</link><description>本特别通讯描述了共享数据和生物样本的障碍，并提出了加强访问和协作的策略。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/enhancing-clinical-cancer-research-through-sharing-of-data-and-biospecimens2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 00:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/enhancing-clinical-cancer-research-through-sharing-of-data-and-biospecimens</guid></item><item><title>向配子发生过渡时的基因组重组</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/genomic-reorganization-at-the-transition-to-gametogenesis</link><description>研究小组使用一种名为 Hi-C 分析的技术来观察 DNA 在细胞核内的三维排列方式，发现在这个过渡点，基因组的三维组织变得不那么结构化，染色体在细胞核内变得更加分离。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/genomic-reorganization-at-the-transition-to-gametogenesis2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 00:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/genomic-reorganization-at-the-transition-to-gametogenesis</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥变出“陆上巴拿马运河”：全长303公里，穿越特万特佩克地峡，不经船闸连接太平洋和海湾</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mexico-pulls-a-land-based-panama-canal-out-of-its-hat-303-km-across-the-isthmus-of-tehuantepec-to-connect-the-pacific-and-the-gulf-without-passing-through-locks</link><description>由于干旱扰乱了全球航运，墨西哥推出了一条横跨地峡的 303 公里铁路走廊，以与巴拿马竞争。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mexico-pulls-a-land-based-panama-canal-out-of-its-hat-303-km-across-the-isthmus-of-tehuantepec-to-connect-the-pacific-and-the-gulf-without-passing-through-locks.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 00:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mexico-pulls-a-land-based-panama-canal-out-of-its-hat-303-km-across-the-isthmus-of-tehuantepec-to-connect-the-pacific-and-the-gulf-without-passing-through-locks</guid></item><item><title>MeerKAT 在半个宇宙中发现破纪录的宇宙激光</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/meerkat-discovers-record-breaking-cosmic-laser-halfway-across-the-universe</link><description>天文学家使用南非的 MeerKAT 射电望远镜发现了迄今为止探测到的最遥远的羟基巨型脉泽。它位于一个距离我们超过80亿光年的剧烈合并星系中，开辟了射电天文学的新前沿。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/meerkat-discovers-record-breaking-cosmic-laser-halfway-across-the-universe.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 00:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/meerkat-discovers-record-breaking-cosmic-laser-halfway-across-the-universe</guid></item><item><title>巨大“超级木星”的发现令科学家们困惑不已</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/discovery-of-colossal-super-jupiters-puzzles-scientists</link><description>木星可能是太阳系中的行星之王，但在银河系的其他恒星系统中，甚至更大的行星的轨道距离其恒星数十亿英里——在传统形成理论难以解释的地方。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/discovery-of-colossal-super-jupiters-puzzles-scientists.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 23:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/discovery-of-colossal-super-jupiters-puzzles-scientists</guid></item><item><title>新发现的 85 亿年前的星系为早期宇宙演化提供了罕见的视角</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/newly-discovered-galaxy-from-8-5-billion-years-ago-offers-rare-look-at-early-cosmic-evolution</link><description>一个新发现的星系，其充满恒星的发光“触手”正在改写部分宇宙历史。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/newly-discovered-galaxy-from-8-5-billion-years-ago-offers-rare-look-at-early-cosmic-evolution2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 23:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/newly-discovered-galaxy-from-8-5-billion-years-ago-offers-rare-look-at-early-cosmic-evolution</guid></item><item><title>外星人复活和现代普罗米修斯</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/alien-reanimation-and-the-modern-prometheus</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 23:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/alien-reanimation-and-the-modern-prometheus</guid></item><item><title>对大脑增强的探索，尤其是涉及神经尘埃的大脑增强</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/an-exploration-of-brain-augmentation-especially-that-which-involves-neural-dust</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 23:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/an-exploration-of-brain-augmentation-especially-that-which-involves-neural-dust</guid></item><item><title>无敌套娃大脑星际帝国</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-invincible-matrioshka-brain-star-empire</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 22:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-invincible-matrioshka-brain-star-empire</guid></item></channel></rss>